                        <figcaption itemprop="caption">Indigenous athletes shining in Taiwan's women's baseball league.<br><small>Photo by <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:11.30_%E5%89%AF%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E3%80%8C2025%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E6%A3%92%E7%90%83%E8%81%AF%E8%B3%BD%E9%96%89%E5%B9%95%E6%9A%A8%E9%A0%92%E7%8D%8E%E5%85%B8%E7%A6%AE%E3%80%8D_-_54953847137.jpg" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Taiwan Presidential Office</a> / <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">CC BY 4.0</a></small></figcaption>
